# FluentUp — English Language Academy Website

A multi-page website for FluentUp, an English language academy. Built with HTML, Bootstrap 5, and custom CSS.

## Project structure

```
fluentup/
├── index.html            Home page (hero, stats, features, courses preview, testimonial, CTA)
├── about.html            Story, values, teaching approach, instructors
├── services.html         Group classes, private lessons, exam prep, corporate training
├── courses.html          Full course catalog with filter tags
├── course-details.html   Single-course template (outline, price, instructor)
├── exams.html            IELTS vs. TOEFL comparison and exam prep details
├── contact.html          Contact form and info cards
├── css/
│   └── style.css         All custom styles (variables, layout, components)
├── js/
│   ├── bootstrap.bundle.min.js
│   └── all.min.js        Font Awesome JS
└── img/                  Local image assets (currently using picsum.photos placeholders)
```

## Requirements

This project depends on local copies of:
- `css/bootstrap.min.css`
- `js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js`
- `js/all.min.js` (Font Awesome)

Download these and place them in the matching folders before running the site — the pages reference them via relative paths.

**Fonts and icons loaded from CDN** (already wired up, no setup needed):
- Google Fonts — Kameron (headings) + Roboto (body)
- Font Awesome 6.5.2 (icons)

## Running locally

Open `index.html` directly in a browser, or — recommended — serve it with a local server so relative paths and any future JS behave consistently:

- **VS Code**: install the "Live Server" extension, right-click `index.html` → "Open with Live Server"
- **Python**: `python -m http.server 8000` from the project folder, then visit `http://localhost:8000`

## Design system

| Token | Value | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `--dark-color` | `#19283f` | Navbar, hero sections, footer |
| `--green-color` | `#33d1cc` | Primary accent, buttons, highlights |
| `--cream-color` | `#f7f4ef` | Light section backgrounds |
| `--coral-color` | `#ff8a65` | Reserved secondary accent |
| `--text-muted` | `#6b7280` | Body copy on light backgrounds |

Headings use **Kameron** (serif), body text uses **Roboto**.

## Known placeholders (replace before launch)

- **Images** — all photos currently use `picsum.photos` stock placeholders. Replace with real, licensed photos of the academy, instructors, and students.
- **Instructor names/bios** — placeholder names in `about.html` and `course-details.html`.
- **Course content** — pricing, outlines, and descriptions are illustrative; only one course (`course-details.html`) has a full template. Duplicate it per course.
- **Contact form** — `contact.html` has no backend wired up. It needs a form handler (e.g. Formspree, Netlify Forms) or a custom backend to actually receive submissions.
- **Course filter tags** on `courses.html` are visual only — filtering by level isn't functional yet without JavaScript.
- **Social links, address, phone number** in the footer are placeholders.

## Pages still to build (optional)

- Individual course detail pages per course (rather than one shared template)
- A blog or resources section, if desired
- 404 / error page

